The kismet source package is split into several packages:

kismet:
	This is the metapackage: it installs the Kismet packages.
kismet-core:
	This is the core of kismet.
kismet-capture-*:
	These packages contain capture helpers. They don't require
	kismet-core to be used.
python3-kismet*:
	Theses packages contain capture driver in Python 3.
kismet-plugins:
	This package contains some extra plugins for kismet.
